{"tid":2105744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇 當年六四 大量受過中國教育既中國人移民澳洲 中共冇反對","createTime":"2020-07-13T00:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T00:55:59.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f301eff19be4b418d4f67c95d02aae7159128829","tid":2105744,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:30:01.000Z","msg":"點睇當年六四，大量受過中國教育既中國人移民澳洲或美英國 ，<br />\n<br />\n單單係澳洲立即收了幾萬中國人，但中共冇反對 ，<br />\n<br />\n而且當年香港人更加<span class=\"red\">出了大量錢幫助中國示威者移民西方</span>，<br />\n<br />\n香港人還公開感謝西方大量收留中國同胞。<br />\n<br />\n當年受過香港人幫助移民到西方既中國人，但冇幾多個在香港反送中運動中公開支持香港人？<br />\n<br />\n但現在全中國人眼紅香港人可以移民去西方，出盡外交力量去阻止香港平民人移民西方？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進質疑內地14億民眾冇份 只開放香港人移民西方人虛偽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tConFCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtConFCv.jpg&h=e0daeb96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2693252/【BNO】胡錫進諷西方虛偽：為何只放寬港人移民%20%2014億內地人無份？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2693252%2F%E3%80%90BNO%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E8%AB%B7%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E8%99%9B%E5%81%BD%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%8F%AA%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%2520%252014%E5%84%84%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%9F&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZoszBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=6fe12769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2693252/【BNO】胡錫進諷西方虛偽：為何只放寬港人移民%20%2014億內地人無份？</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n央視擔心：BNO黃絲去英國或要做辛苦工，叫大家要想清楚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2097164/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2097164/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n人民日報公開批香港人為何不堂正做中國人？而去做低端人口<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2685000/2689142/0707_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2685000%2F2689142%2F0707_1024.jpg&h=c3a9c739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2689142/?lcc=ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2689142%2F%3Flcc%3Dac&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZoszBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=d649ba70\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2689142/?lcc=ac</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八九學運與香港時代革命的比較<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z_Bz3Q8tOig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ_Bz3Q8tOig&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZoszBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=74d45ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z_Bz3Q8tOig</a>"},{"pid":"8137f4baec44580aa5fbb07f8f7300d3034701ee","tid":2105744,"uid":30561,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">上佢地內地forum睇，唔少人覺得中央唔夠硬<br />\n<br />\n話有bno就應該要即刻剝奪香港籍<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住過完國安法，心理上可以將香港人拉落去陪葬<br />\n<br />\n點知英國，5眼又大開逃生門俾港豬移民，突然昇lv<br />\n<br />\n你叫中國人條氣點頂得順<br />\n<br />\n係佢地眼中，每一個香港人都係英國狗<br />\n<br />\n霸住佢地心中「中國」香港但又有西方價值觀嘅都應該要捉<br />\n<br />\n留島唔留人呢種觀念係大陸人心中根深蒂固好多年<br />\n<br />\n講過好多次，就算大陸今時今日大國堀起<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">但係大陸人心裡面從來冇當香港人係同胞</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人永遠係大陸人嘅心魔，死症嚟<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"55a617cca2c781954191441fab4491632f134ed4","tid":2105744,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b86c65ab65ad0bfd8ba67a010bdfd5a8d170f8b2","tid":2105744,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8137f4baec44580aa5fbb07f8f7300d3034701ee","tid":2105744,"uid":30561,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">上佢地內地forum睇，唔少人覺得中央唔夠硬<br />\n<br />\n話有bno就應該要即刻剝奪香港籍<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住過完國安法，心理上可以將香港人拉落去陪葬<br />\n<br />\n點知英國，5眼又大開逃生門俾港豬移民，突然昇lv<br />\n<br />\n你叫中國人條氣點頂得順<br />\n<br />\n係佢地眼中，每一個香港人都係英國狗<br />\n<br />\n霸住佢地心中